PRIVATE EVENTS
Thank you for considering us for your upcoming event! Our commitment is to deliver exceptional food, balanced cocktails, and a unique ambiance, ensuring your celebration is the most memorable one since your sweet sixteen. You're invited to gather at our tables with the warmth and welcome you'd find in our own home.
Our private event pricing is a food and beverage (F&B) minimum spend based on historical revenue for that time of year and day of the week you host your event.
What is a F&B minimum? It is the amount you are required to spend on food and beverages to use our space and it takes the place of a room rental fee if you reach that minimum.
